据报道，特雷西·查普曼将在格莱美颁奖典礼上与卢克·库姆斯一起表演《Fast Car》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/tracy-chapman-reportedly-set-to-perform-fast-car-with-luke-combs-at-grammys-3580446?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=tracy-据报道，查普曼将在格莱美颁奖典礼上与卢克·库姆斯一起表演《快车》Hollie Geraghty Thu, 01 Feb 2024 09:13:08 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryGrammys https://www.nme.com/?p=3580446 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="特雷西·查普曼，卢克·库姆斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位艺术家 1988 年的歌曲通过去年的热门翻唱获得了新的生命</p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tracy-chapman-reportedly-set-to-perform-fast-car-with-luke-combs-at-grammys-3580446">，特雷西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman) 将在格莱美颁奖典礼上与卢克·库姆斯 (Luke Combs) 一起表演《Fast Car》，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="特雷西·查普曼，卢克·库姆斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tracy-chapman">特雷西·查普曼</a>将于本周在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美颁奖典礼</a>上与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/luke-combs">卢克·库姆斯</a>一起表演《Fast Car》。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/tracy-chapman-luke-combs-grammys-perform-1235891995/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《Variety》</a></em>杂志的消息人士透露，这位以 1988 年歌曲《Fast Car》而闻名的美国创作歌手将在周日（2 月 5 日）的颁奖典礼上与库姆斯一起表演二重唱。</p><p>库姆斯去年翻唱了这首经典歌曲，一经发行便大受欢迎， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-scott-burna-boy-and-luke-combs-to-perform-at-2024-grammys-3574748">并于上周被宣布为表演者</a>。</p><p>这次二重唱标志着查普曼罕见地重返舞台，自 2009 年结束上一次巡演以来，查普曼只在镜头前表演过几次。</p><p>去年，她创造了乡村音乐历史，当时她的 35 年歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tracy-chapman-makes-country-music-history-3535074">在纳什维尔举行的 2023 年颁奖典礼上同时被评为年度歌曲和年度单曲</a>。这一认可使查普曼成为该奖项 57 年历史上第一位获得年度歌曲奖的黑人歌曲作者。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Luke Combs - Fast Car（官方现场视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Fr7oYjnt3bM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <em>Variety</em>未能联系到唱片学院的代表置评。</p><p>库姆斯的《Fast Car》在官方排行榜前 40<a href="https://www.officialcharts.com/songs/luke-combs-fast-car/">名中排名第七</a>，去年查普曼分享了她对这位乡村音乐明星翻唱歌曲的支持。</p><p> “我从没想过自己会出现在乡村音乐排行榜上，但我很荣幸能在那里，”查普曼在一份声明中告诉<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/country/tracy-chapman-reacts-luke-combs-fast-car-cover-1235367446/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">公告牌</a></em>。 “我为卢克和他的成功感到高兴，并感谢新粉丝发现并接受了《快车》。”</p><p>库姆斯本人告诉<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/country/luke-combs-reacts-tracy-chapmans-fast-car-shout-out-1235372985/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《公告牌》</a></em> ，这首歌“让我惊讶得超乎你的想象”。</p><p> “特雷西·查普曼（Tracy Chapman）写了这首完美的歌曲，我第一次是和我爸爸一起听的，自从我在现场表演中演奏这首歌六年多以来，它就一直伴随着我，所有这些体育场的每个人——我是说每个人——都与这首歌有关并跟着唱。这是超自然歌曲作家的天赋，”他补充道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Tracy Chapman - Fast Car（官方音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AIOAlaACuv4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我的封面的成功是不真实的，我认为特蕾西得到认可并达到了新的里程碑真是太酷了。我喜欢她在那里感受到所有的爱，并且她向我大声喊叫！谢谢你，特蕾西！”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">Olivia Rodrigo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/burna-boy">Burna Boy</a>也将在洛杉矶 Crypto.com Arena 举办的格莱美颁奖典礼上表演。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/trevor-noah-to-host-2024-grammys-3559098#:~:text=Trevor%20Noah%20has%20been%20announced,in%20which%20he%20has%20hosted.&amp;text=The%20former%20Daily%20Show%20host,in%20both%202019%20and%202020.">特雷弗·诺亚将连续第四年主持该奖项</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift</a> )、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> 、维多利亚<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/victoria-monet">·莫奈 (Victoria Monet</a> ) 和菲比·布里杰斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">Phoebe Bridgers)</a>领衔今年的提名 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-grammys-2024-nominations-3536101" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处查看完整名单</a>。</p><p>据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tracy-chapman-reportedly-set-to-perform-fast-car-with-luke-combs-at-grammys-3580446">，特雷西·查普曼 (Tracy Chapman) 将在格莱美颁奖典礼上与卢克·库姆斯 (Luke Combs) 一起表演《Fast Car》，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
